strings.Value: "A whole world free of wilting and sorrow. A world untouched by Groetus! What we have seen is truly impressive."
"He's impressed! As if you'd found an eye-witness to the greatest event in the history of your people, and all you managed to get out of him was some disjointed gibberish!"
"Hope you found food for thought, and not another field to sow your dark ideas."
"An amazing place... and equally amazing inhabitants. Well, now I know where I'll set off to, once I've grown hopelessly bored of everything here."
